Latest Canadian Numbers on SARS (Health Canada)
"Active" cases include those hospitalized, currently ill at home, or
under investigation.
Active SARS cases in Canada
Date: May 23 / May 25/ May 26/ May 27/ May 28/ May 29/ May 30/ Jun 2/
